OL,3,CMan charged with murder following
OL,4,Cdeath of Doncaster man
OL,6,FA 53-year-old man has been charged
OL,7,Fwith murder after another man was
OL,8,Ffound with serious knife injuries in
OL,9,FDoncaster.
OL,11,FOn Friday, 10 July, at 7pm South
OL,12,FYorkshire Police received reports of
OL,13,Fan injured man in Wordsworth Avenue in
OL,14,Fthe Balby area of Doncaster.
OL,16,FA 32-year-old man was found with a
OL,17,Fserious knife injury and was taken to
OL,18,Fhospital where he later died.
OL,20,FPeter Norburn, aged 53, of no fixed
OL,21,Fabode, is charged with murder.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/2
